{"title":"hex to rgb converter","description":"A program that allows you to quickly convert hex to rgb online.","content":"## About hex to rgb converter\r\nThis converter allows you to convert the color value of the **HEX** color model to **RGbB**\r\nAs a result of the conversion, you will get three numbers, each of which indicates the degree of presence of red, green and blue.\r\nValues ​​are represented by a range of numbers from 0 to 256\r\nThis program can also perform reverse conversion, that is, [convert rgb to hex](/en/color/rgb_to_hex).\r\n\r\n## How to convert hex to rgb\r\nTo perform the conversion, enter the hex value in the corresponding line instead of the current color.\r\nThe **RGB** value will be immediately calculated and displayed in three fields for each primary color: red, green and blue."}